General.Name: Shoe Zone PLC
General.Description: Shoe Zone plc operates as a footwear retailer in the United Kingdom and the Republic of Ireland. The company offers shoes for men, women, boys, and girls. It offers product through stores and shoezone.com, a Website. Shoe Zone plc was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Leicester, the United Kingdom.
General.Address: Haramead Business Centre, Leicester, United Kingdom, LE1 2LH
